commit.message:
New agent with CNN model

Solved input error to model where only one row of pixels was served as input. Now 240x256x3 pixels are inputs. 
Updated the model to a CNN with 2 convolutional layers, 2 max pooling layers, a flattening layer, and a dense layer.
Should perform better.
